  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into fries</p><p>Add the<strong> fries</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1691059454569-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1691059454569-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1691059454569-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1691059454569-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1691059454569-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fries are cooking, slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> finely into rounds</p><p>Add the <strong>cucumber rounds</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>cider vinegar</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>warm water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Mix it all together and set aside – these are your <strong>quick-pickles</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1691059457175-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1691059457175-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1691059457175-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1691059457175-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1691059457175-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> into rings</p><p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>into rounds</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1691059459673-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1691059459673-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1691059459673-x700.jpg",
