            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mustard ketchup</strong>, <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>ketchup</strong> in a bowl with 1/2 tsp per person<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>of your <strong>pickling liquid </strong>from the bowl of pickles</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>burger sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1691059462112-x200.jpg",
