          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1691059462112-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>beef mince</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for a further 6 min or until cooked through (no pink meat) and slightly crisp</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1691059464844-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1691059464844-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1691059464844-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1691059464844-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1691059464844-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked through and slightly crisp, gently push the <strong>cooked mince</strong> into the centre of pan</p><p>Top the mince with the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and cook, covered, for a final 2-3 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>cheesy beef</strong></p><p>Pierce your<strong> bao bun packet[s]</strong> with a few holes and <strong>microwave</strong> for 1-2 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1691059468137-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1691059468137-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1691059468137-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1691059468137-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
