          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1691059468137-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, load each bao bun with a little <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, a <strong>tomato round</strong>,<strong> shallot rings </strong>and some of the <strong>quick-pickles</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>cheesy beef </strong>and drizzle over a spoonful of the <strong>burger sauce</strong> – these are your <strong>cheeseburger bao buns</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
