            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cheeseburger bao buns </strong>with the <strong>fries</strong> and any <strong>remaining shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>quick-pickles</strong> and <strong>burger sauce</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
